14. Seal Sentence

NATT-OS is not AGI.

NATT-OS is a governed operating architecture that protects identity, memory, state, boundary, signal, audit, and continuity so that runtime entities and system assets are not reduced to prompts, model versions, recipes, caches, or unaudited outputs.
